| Component | ESP32 Pin | Notes                                 |
| --------- | --------- | ------------------------------------- |
| White LED | GPIO 25   | Add 220 Ω resistor to ground          |
| Green LED | GPIO 33   | add 220 Ω resistor to ground         |
| LCD SDA   | GPIO 21   | Default I²C data                      |
| LCD SCL   | GPIO 22   | Default I²C clock                     |
| Buzzer    | GPIO 23   | As in code                            |
| LCD VCC   | 5 V       | or 3.3 V if marked “3.3 V compatible” |
| LCD GND   | GND       | Common ground                         |

Turn the blue potentiometer on the small PCB on the back of the LCD to adjust text visibility.

Courtesy of my friend at chatgpt

